          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="p-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-primary-800 mb-2">Community Transformation</h3>
          <p class="text-earth-600 mb-4">We foster holistic transformation through literacy programs, community development, and sustainable initiatives.</p>
          <a href="#stories" class="text-primary-700 hover:text-primary-900 font-medium inline-flex items-center">
            Learn more
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4 ml-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7" />
            </svg>
